    pageItem P320_ABSTRACT (
        type: richTextEditor
        label {
            label: Workshop Abstract
            alignment: left
        }
        settings {
            format: html
            minHeight: 220
            maxHeight: 220
        }
        layout {
            sequence: 50
            region: @content-details
            slot: regionBody
            alignment: left
        }
        appearance {
            template: @required-above
            templateOptions: #DEFAULT#
        }
        source {
            formRegion: @workshop-details
            column: ABSTRACT
            dataType: varchar2
        }
        default {
            type: static
            staticValue:
                ```
                <ul><li><b>Workshop Elevator Pitch/Messaging</b>:  Required </li>
                <li><b>Workshop Description</b>:  Required</li>
                <li><b>Why is this workshop needed?</b> Please fill in</li>
                <li><b>What products/technologies are used? </b> Please fill in</li>
                <li><b>Is there a primary Oracle product/technology being showcased?  If so, what is it? </b> Needed for Workshop Council</li>
                </ul>
                <br>
                For OSPA Workshops Only:
                <ul><li><b>What are the training objectives?</b> Please fill in</li>
                <li><b>What module will this exist in?</b> Please fill in </li>
                </ul>
                
                ```
        }
        help {
            helpText: This field is what is used for approval by the workshop council. Workshops are reviewed by the workshop council for adherence to current Oracle messaging.  If you don't put enough detail, the council may kick it back and delay your workshop.
        }
    )

