            helpText:
                ```html
                Click this checkbox to verify that each lab has Tasks (##) below the fold, the task content is initial capitalized (not bold), and there's a colon between task number and task title. <br>
                ✅ Task 1: Log into Cloud Account<br>
                
                ❌ Task 1: Log into Cloud Account<br>
                ❌ Task 1: Log into Cloud Account<br>
                ❌ Task 1: LOG INTO CLOUD ACCOUNT<br>
                ❌ TASK 1: Log into Cloud Account<br>
                ❌ Task 1: Log into cloud account<br>
                ❌ Task 1 - Log into Cloud Account<br>
                
                ```
        }
    )

    pageItem P320_LAB_TITLE_1 (
